{"tid":1581861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日有個活動 大家冇理由唔去支持下","createTime":"2019-09-19T18:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T19:53:56.000Z","uid":292410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a1951d65c7b04c5b1b332327d98f7a75ec3803","tid":1581861,"uid":292410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"📢📣《銀髪族響應罷買行動Bye Buy Day》響應罷買日第四擊<br />\n<br />\n《窗櫥遊走 攰就抖抖》<br />\n銀髮族夏日消暑商場巡演<br />\n<br />\n第四站：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年9月20日（星期五）<br />\n時間：下午四時至八時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀海港城公共空間<br />\n🎏逢正點遊走各層<br />\n🎈在連儂牆表達意見<br />\n🎈小風扇要帶，公共空間在室外<br />\n🎈歡迎任何人士一同參與<br />\n<br />\n罷買有冇用？<br />\n每星期罷買唔消費係會對商家、政權分別因為利潤受損和經濟停滯不前而面對壓力，促使商家督促政府去回應市民嘅訴求！<br />\n<br />\n我哋唔知道呢個方法係咪一定成功。我哋要做嘅就係盡一切可行方法去爭取政府正面回應我哋嘅訴求!<br />\n<br />\n罷買成功與否在乎人數!<br />\n罷買成唔成功在乎市民嘅決心!<br />\n<br />\n百萬港人，一齊努力！<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/891122997933192?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F891122997933192%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=f70c5c0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/891122997933192?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ac457dc16d7c50d8e9098c4be3dd096e7fcc6244","tid":1581861,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"PISH<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a89dd40082eada77b89138467ae96a6e8da867","tid":1581861,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T18:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d46b499e4ad3ba7784735bd362e677b614e2a77","tid":1581861,"uid":304180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB